          "_type": "span",
          "text": "…is a wonderful sounding phrase for a (potentially) disastrous action.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s defined as a “taking a substantially dangerous (possibly lethal) risk.”",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "To try to beat the light (on a bike). To surf a tsunami. Or steal honey from an African honey bee.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Thing is, most ‘risks’ in life aren’t lethal. They just feel like they are.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Speaking up in a meeting. Going to that party. Starting a business. Changing your job. Asking someone out. These things won’t kill you.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "In fact, if you get a bad outcome (the worst case scenario), you’ll likely (soon) find a way to recover.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Hence, the beauty the phrase, “",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "non",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " salto mortale.” Literally, not fatal.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What a great way to remind yourself you can’t die trying.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}